</emphasis>
, paratypes from Amazonas. 
<emphasis id="B96E2E5B7953FF9FBDB77956CBCBF885" bold="true" box="[902,955,1859,1883]" pageId="10" pageNumber="49">A–F,</emphasis>
male; 
<emphasis id="B96E2E5B7953FF9FBA357956CC67F885" bold="true" box="[1028,1047,1859,1883]" pageId="10" pageNumber="49">A</emphasis>
, wing; 
<emphasis id="B96E2E5B7953FF9FBA567956CC09F885" bold="true" box="[1127,1145,1859,1883]" pageId="10" pageNumber="49">B</emphasis>
, tergite 8, dorsal view with right setae omitted; 
<emphasis id="B96E2E5B7953FF9FBF427973C9F6F8A0" bold="true" box="[371,390,1894,1918]" pageId="10" pageNumber="49">C</emphasis>
, terminalia, lateral view; 
<emphasis id="B96E2E5B7953FF9FBC957973CAC7F8A0" bold="true" box="[676,695,1894,1918]" pageId="10" pageNumber="49">D</emphasis>
, detail of posterior cercus; 
<emphasis id="B96E2E5B7953FF9FBDD67973CB89F8A0" bold="true" box="[999,1017,1894,1918]" pageId="10" pageNumber="49">E</emphasis>
